, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">Kanye West</a> has declared that he&#39;s “not a Nazi” after a string of anti-Semitic social media posts earlier this month.</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-unaired-footage-fox-news-anti-semitic-comments-3326989">With his “White Lives Matter” stunt, has Kanye West finally hit the point of no return?</a></strong></li></ul><p> On Wednesday night (February 19), the controversial rapper took to X (formerly Twitter) to share that “after further reflection”, he&#39;s “come to the realisation that I&#39;m not a Nazi”.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> After further reflection I&#39;ve come to the realization that I&#39;m not a Nazi</p><p> — ye (@kanyewest) <a href="https://twitter.com/kanyewest/status/1892307950670057946?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 19, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> The post comes after the &#39;Gold Digger&#39; rapper <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">launched a string of highly controversial posts on the social media platform earlier this month</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">sold a swastika t-shirt on his website</a> before it was taken down.</p><p> His posting spree – which began after the Grammys earlier this month – saw him <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">rescind his apology to the Jewish community for his past anti-Semitic remarks</a> , and go on to declare himself as “a Nazi” and write: “I love Hitler”, as well as praise billionaire and X owner <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">Elon Musk</a> as “the most lit person that [has] ever been on Twitter”, following <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">the latter&#39;s accusations of Nazism at Donald Trump&#39;s presidential inauguration</a> .</p><p> Further posts saw him mock other marginalised communities, claim that “slavery is a choice” and more. He then wiped his Yeezy website and began selling <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">a white T-shirt with a large swastika emblem on the chest</a> , listed as “HH-01” on his website – possibly a reference to the “Heil Hitler” chant.</p><p> The site was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">later taken down by Shopify</a> , though the online retailer later <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-says-kanye-wests-site-was-removed-over-fraud-potential-not-swastika-t-shirt-3837621">stated that the artist&#39;s website was taken down due to the potential for fraud – not because it was selling a swastika t-shirt</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3838836" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3838836" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3838836" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3838836" class="wp-caption-text"> Kanye West in 2019. Credit: Gilbert Carrasquillo/GC Images</figcaption></figure><p> The spree saw <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-x-account-has-been-deactivated-after-bizarre-weekend-rant-3836418">his X account taken down and deactivated</a> , and it was later confirmed that the rapper had <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dropped-by-talent-agency-following-anti-semitic-posts-3837245">been dropped by his talent agency,</a> and his former Chief Of Staff had quit the Yeezy company.</p><p> Kanye West&#39;s X account was later reinstated, through which the rapper has since said he&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-had-swastika-t-shirt-idea-for-over-eight-years-3838835">had the idea for the t-shirt for “over eight years”</a> . He also recently that his last “rampage” was “90 per cent Jew proof” before going on to hint at his <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanyes-twitter-and-instagram-accounts-locked-after-antisemitic-posts-3325446">infamous anti-Semitic tirade a couple of years back</a> that among many other outlandish claims, saw him tell the Jewish community that they needed to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-tells-jewish-people-to-forgive-hitler-compares-porn-to-the-holocaust-3361860">“forgive Hitler”</a> for the holocaust – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-apologises-jewish-community-antisemitic-comments-3563267">he apologised for his comments back in 2023</a> .</p><p> His rants earlier this month also saw him <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">declare “dominion” over his wife Bianca Censori</a> after they attended the Grammys red carpet event, where <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-kanye-west-shows-up-with-wife-bianca-censori-who-reveals-shocking-see-through-dress-3833867">she wore a see-through dress that revealed her naked figure</a> . He also posted a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-voices-support-for-diddy-and-chris-brown-free-puff-3835815">series of tweets in support of Diddy and Chris Brown and urged for the former to be released from prison amid sexual abuse allegations</a> .</p><p> In the time since the rant on social media, Kanye West&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">&#39;Vultures&#39;</a> collaborator <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ty-dolla-ign-condemns-hate-speech-following-kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-and-swastika-t-shirt-controversy-3837549">Ty Dolla $ign has condemned his hate speech</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlie-puth-begs-kanye-west-to-stop-promoting-incredibly-dangerous-messages-and-swastika-tee-3837062">Charlie Puth begged West to stop promoting “incredibly dangerous” messages,</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>Friends</em></a> star <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-schwimmer-calls-for-action-against-kanye-west-after-nazi-comments-silence-is-complicity-3836363">David Schwimmer called for action to be taken against the rapper</a> for his hate-filled “Nazi” posts, arguing that “silence is complicity”.</p><p> Elsewhere, Ye has been <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-sued-for-discrimination-and-accused-of-texting-hail-hitler-to-jewish-yeezy-employee-3837691">sued for discrimination by a former Yeezy employee, and accused of texting “Hail Hitler” to a Jewish staff member</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-has-come-to-the-realisation-that-hes-not-a-nazi-after-reflection-3839623">Kanye West has “come to the realisation” that he&#39;s “not a Nazi” after “reflection”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
谢菲尔德的Leadmill失去了与房东的驱逐法庭之战 - 但誓言要战斗https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffields-leadmill-leadmill-loses-eviction-court-battle-with-landlord-landlord-but-vow-to to-fight-3839619?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = sheffields-leadmill-loses-loses-roses-court-court-court-battle-with-landlord-blandlord-but-but-to-vow-to-to-to-to-on-OnSurej Singh Thu, 20 Feb 2025 02:14:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3839619 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="在谢菲尔德的Leadmill在那里Def Leppard进行了“仅一晚”演出。图片日期：2023年5月19日，星期五。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>建筑所有者在2022年发出了驱逐通知</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffields-leadmill-loses-eviction-court-battle-with-landlord-but-vow-to-fight-on-3839619">谢菲尔德后的领导台失去了与房东的驱逐法庭之战 - 但誓言</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="在谢菲尔德的Leadmill在那里Def Leppard进行了“仅一晚”演出。图片日期：2023年5月19日，星期五。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>谢菲尔德（Sheffield）的Leadmill与房东失去了驱逐法庭的战斗，使其未来的不确定 - 标志性的现场发表了一份声明，承诺将继续战斗。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/sheffield-leadmill-arctic-monkeys-closes-we-all-lose-something-3196736"><b>如果谢菲尔德的Leadmill（有助于破坏北极猴子的场所）走了，我们都失去了一些东西</b></a></li></ul><p>Electric Group是900个容量的地点大楼的所有者， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">于2022年3月向Leadmill Ltd发出了驱逐通知</a>，这引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">音乐界和演出者的强烈抗议</a>。 Leadmill Ltd拥有场地名称的商标 - 这意味着不同建筑物中的新场地可以保留原件的名称和品牌。</p><p>自1980年首次开业以来，该场地已经举办了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">北极猴子</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">莱昂国王</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">杀手</a>的早期表演，并且仍然是流行的现场音乐和俱乐部。</p><p>昨晚（2月19日），Leadmill在社交媒体上发表了一份声明，内容涉及法院针对该场地的裁决，以支持其房东。 Leadmill写道：“虽然这对我们的场地来说是一个充满挑战和令人沮丧的时刻，但我们希望向支持者，艺术家和更广泛的社区保证，接下来发生的事情没有立即的时间表。” </p><figure id="attachment_3286984" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3286984" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3286984" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3286984" class="wp-caption-text">理查德·霍利（Richard Hawley）和贾维斯·科克（Jarvis Cocker）在2022年8月9日在谢菲尔德（Sheffield）的Leadmill舞台上。</figcaption></figure><p> Leadmill说，目前没有明确的道路前进，它正在“积极咨询”其法律顾问，并“将继续致力于耗尽一切可能的法律途径，以确保我们的未来，保留我们的员工并保护我们的场地。”</p><p>法院的战斗不仅是为了拯救场地，还说：“这是个人的。 Leadmill不仅仅是砖和砂浆。这是一个家。我们的许多团队在这里长大，在这里工作了15年以上，并致力于创造令人难以置信的活动和经验。我们是真实的人，对我们所做的事情充满了热爱，而且我们从来没有成像过这样的事情。但是我们在一起，竭尽所能为对我们和许多其他人来说意义重大的地方而战。”</p><p> Leadmill指出自驱逐新闻首次爆发以来，该场地的文化影响及其获得的支持，重申了它的“不仅仅是一个场地”：“这是一个具有45年培养艺术家历史的文化机构，支持艺术家的历史基层音乐，并为谢菲尔德及其他地区提供了重要的创造力。”</p><p>该场地还向顾客和任何有门票的人确认，除非另有说明，否则所有计划编程将按计划进行的节目和活动。</p><p>在结束的讲话中，Leadmill敦促其支持者“继续与我们站在一起”，因为他们“在这场战斗的下一个阶段中导航”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGREpiRzatI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 